HOUSE BILL NO. HB0214
Local government payments-electronic payments.
Sponsored by: Representative(s) Thayer, Davis, Geringer,
Heiner, Larson, JT, Lawley and Sherwood and
Senator(s) Barlow and Crum
A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to cities, towns and counties; authorizing
2 local governments to pay claims and demands through
3 electronic payment means; making conforming amendments; and
4 providing for an effective date.
5
6 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
7
8 Section 1. W.S. 15-1-125(b), 15-4-302(a),
9 18-3-511(a), 18-3-810 and 18-3-811 are amended to read:
10
11 15-1-125. Presentation and payment of claims; when
12 warrant draws interest; exception.
13
14 (b) Upon the allowance of any claim or demand by the
15 governing body, the treasurer shall issue a check or
